        "4. **Tax Calculator:**\n",
        "    - Depending on the amount of income, people are taxed at different rates.\n",
        "    - Income up to $10,000: No tax, Income $10,001-$50,000: 10% tax, Income $50,001 and above: 20% tax.\n",
        "    - Ask the user for their income and calculate the tax they owe.\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "4RMhCDsXRPTO"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "income = float(input(\"Please enter your income: \"))\n",
        "\n",
        "no = 0\n",
        "ten = 0.10\n",
        "twenty = 0.20\n",
        "\n",
        "if income <= 10000:\n",
        "    owed = income * no\n",
        "elif income <= 50000:\n",
        "    owed = 10000 * no + (income - 10000) * ten\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    owed = 10000 * no + 40000 * ten + (income - 50000) * twenty\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"The tax you owe is $\",owed)\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ijEDRr8FRSm0",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "outputId": "d59ff16a-bcf1-4921-8a1b-038b5c5c8315"
      },
      "execution_count": 9,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Please enter your income: 100\n",
            "The tax you owe is $ 0.0\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
