        "5. **Discount Eligibility:**\n",
        "    - A store offers a discount to students and senior citizens.\n",
        "    - Ask the user if they are a student or a senior citizen (yes or no for each). If they answer \"yes\" to either, inform them they are eligible for a discount.\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "qonCcp_PRTDL"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
